overview:
After leaving University I spent a number of years in Property Development in the UK, having completed a number of projects and living in dust and rubble for too long I followed a lifelong passion and became a Professional Sailor, delivering luxury yachts across Europe and the USA.

Since moving to Australia in 2007 I have enjoyed an extremely successful career in online sales and search exposure. Seeing a gap in the online market for a non-discounting sales and promotion platform I founded Wynge.com.au. A model that allows suppliers to provide a buying incentive without discounting, maintaining their market pricing point and brand positioning in addition to generating increased sales and exposure.
